high_descs: Turn around and walk to the white table.
Pick up the head of lettuce from the white table.
Turn around and walk to the fridge on the right.
Open the fridge door, place the lettuce on the second shelf, close the door, open the door, take the lettuce out of the fridge, and close the door.
Turn around and face the waste basket to the left of the table.
Put the lettuce inside of the waste bin.
anns.task_desc: To chill a head of lettuce and place in the waste basket.

high_descs: Turn left then turn left again and go to the table
Pick up the green lettuce from the table
Turn left and go to the door then turn left and go to the fridge
Put the lettuce in the fridge, wait a bit, then take the lettuce out of the fridge
Turn around towards the garbage can
Throw the lettuce in the garbage can
anns.task_desc: Put the chilled lettuce in the garbage can

high_descs: Turn to the left toward the sink, then make another left toward the table. Walk toward the table.
Pick up the head of lettuce off of the table.
Turn to the left and walk toward the door, then turn left again and walk toward the fridge.
Open the fridge and place the lettuce on the second shelf. Close the fridge door. Open the fridge door again and take the lettuce out. Close the fridge door again.
Turn all the way around toward the chair by the table and walk toward the chair.
Throw the head of lettuce into the trash can to the left of the chair.
anns.task_desc: Put the head of lettuce into the fridge, take it out and throw it in the trashcan.
